description: Citrine Global Corp. operates as a plant-based wellness and pharma solutions company. It focuses on developing plant-based products to enhance quality of life, and complementary solutions for balancing side effects caused by using medicines, cannabis, treatments, or an unbalanced lifestyle. The company was formerly known as TechCare Corp. and changed its name to Citrine Global Corp. in August 2020. Citrine Global Corp. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Herzliya, Israel.
